_json.gridTitle: Travel inspiration brought to you by holiday experts American Sky
_json.description: Top 10 things to do in New England. Across the globe the ever-changing natural world conjures up a colourful display of seasonal beauty as leaves turn from green to gold and blossom explodes into a thick blanket of pink and white. One of the most iconic stamping grounds for seasonal photographers and lovers of scenic strolls has to be the region of New England, which can be found squirreled away on the northeast coast of America on the border with Canada
